---
const { 
  title = "INTRODUCING", 
  description = `Utya is a unique meme coin created by the talented designer Egor Zhgun, born on April 17th, 2020. Since its inception, Utya has combined the viral power of Telegram stickers and the emerging NFT culture to form an innovative digital asset ecosystem. The original Utya artwork was first revealed on Behance, which you can explore 
<a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/93658133/Utya-Duck-Telegram-Stickers?locale=en_US" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #ffd527;">here</a>. 
Moreover, the official Telegram website 
<a href="https://telegram.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #ffd527;">hosts a wide collection of Utya stickers</a> that showcase its integral role in Telegram’s vibrant meme culture. Utya continues to grow as a beloved digital icon and a thriving community within the blockchain ecosystem.`,
  gifSrc = "/haha-utya.gif" 
} = Astro.props;
---

<style>
  .block-1-widget {
    display: flex;
    background: rgba(255 255 255 / 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin: 24px auto;
    max-width: 900px;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,160,217,0.5);
    font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive, sans-serif;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .block-1-widget .content {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    padding-right: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .block-1-widget .intro-heading {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .block-1-widget .intro-heading div {
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .block-1-widget .intro-intro {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(141, 82, 193, 1);
  }

  .block-1-widget .intro-name {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: rgba(255, 213, 39, 1);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .block-1-widget .intro-tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: rgba(141, 82, 193, 1);
  }

  .block-1-widget p {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .block-1-widget .gif-container {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .block-1-widget .gif-container img {
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .block-1-widget {
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: auto;
    }
    .block-1-widget .content,
    .block-1-widget .gif-container {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      padding-right: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="block-1-widget" role="region" aria-label="Intro Utya widget">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="intro-heading">
      <div class="intro-intro">{title}</div>
      <div class="intro-name">UTYA</div>
      <div class="intro-tagline">The Face of Telegram’s Meme Culture</div>
    </h2>
    <p class={description}></p>
  </div>
  <div class="gif-container">
    <img src={gifSrc} alt="Funny Utya GIF" />
  </div>
</div>
